To run the test, we use below from Command Line:- mvn test -Dtest=CucumberTestRunner

To run the test, using the filters.. :- mvn test "-Dcucumber.filter.tags=@SingleRun" or mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@SingleRun"

To run the test, using the filters.. :- mvn test -Dcucumber.features="classpath:FeatureFile/placeOrder.feature"
Note:- while running above, do check the tags in CucumberOptions class..